### Change role and create audit log
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users/2/role
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Change status and create audit log
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users/2/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

### View audit logs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/audit-logs?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

